---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Base";
---

<Layout
    title="About Me"
    description="Security professional specializing in offensive security assessments and penetration testing"
    image="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <section class="py-12">
            <h1 class="title text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Security Professional & Tech Enthusiast</h1>
            <div class="text-lg space-y-4">
                <p class="leading-relaxed">
                    As a <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-semibold">security professional</span>, I've dedicated 4 years to discovering business-impacting vulnerabilities across various digital platforms. My expertise lies in conducting thorough offensive security assessments and helping developers and clients understand the impact of these vulnerabilities through detailed remediation guidance.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
            <h2 class="title text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Core Security Expertise</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Application Security</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li>🌐 Web Application Penetration Testing</li>
                        <li>📱 Mobile & Android Security Assessment</li>
                        <li>🔌 API Security Testing</li>
                        <li>💻 Thick Client Application Testing</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Infrastructure & Code</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li>🏢 Internal/External Network Testing</li>
                        <li>📝 Source Code Security Reviews</li>
                        <li>🤖 AI/ML Security Assessment</li>
                        <li>🔍 SDK Security Analysis</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
            <h2 class="title text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Expanding Horizons</h2>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Solution Architecture Journey</h3>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
                    Recently, I've begun exploring the world of solution architecture, where I help organizations:
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
                    <li>🎯 Define technical requirements and solutions</li>
                    <li>🔄 Bridge communication between stakeholders and development teams</li>
                    <li>🛡️ Integrate security considerations from the start</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    This new journey complements my security expertise, allowing me to contribute to both secure and efficient system design.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
